It does not look like the `postinstall` action is implemented end to end. For example, there is the following todo in the code for the offline manifest parser

https://source.chromium.org/chromium/chromium/src/+/main:chrome/updater/win/protocol_parser_xml.cc;l=103

```
} else if (event == "postinstall") {
    // TODO(crbug.com/1286574): Handle postinstall action when Result class
    // implements it.
    return true;
  } else {
    ParseError("Unsupported event type in <action>: %s", event.c_str());
    return false;
  }
```
It is not clear that network installs support the feature either.
